Class GeocoderResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.teamdev.jxmaps.MapObject
      • com.teamdev.jxmaps.GeocoderResult
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class GeocoderResult
extends MapObject
    Contains a single geocoder result retrieved from the geocode server. A geocode request may return multiple result objects.
